  ('prep-hash-maps-find-top-k-frequent-elements::init', 'prep-hash-maps-find-top-k-frequent-elements', 'At the start of a run (Find top K frequent elements), what strategy is established?', 'Top K Frequent: return the  values that appear most often in the array. Plan: count every value, drop each value into a bucket keyed by its count, then sweep buckets from highest count down — that is O(n) time and O(n) space, no sorting needed.', 1),
