  ('prep-math-maximum-split-of-positive-even-integers::init', 'prep-math-maximum-split-of-positive-even-integers', 'At the start of a run (Maximum Split of Positive Even Integers), what strategy is established?', 'Maximum Split of Positive Even Integers: pick as many DISTINCT positive even integers as possible that add up to . Greedily take the smallest unused evens 2, 4, 6, … while they still fit, then patch the remainder onto the last one.', 1),
