  ('prep-stacks-queues-decode-string::complexity', 'prep-stacks-queues-decode-string', 'What are the time and space complexities for "Decode String"?', 'O(n·maxK). O(n). Two stacks: one for counts, one for strings built so far; On `[`: push current count and current string, reset both', 4),
