  ('prep-stacks-queues-implement-queue-with-max::complexity', 'prep-stacks-queues-implement-queue-with-max', 'What are the time and space complexities for "Implement queue with max"?', 'O(1) amortized. O(n). enqueue drops smaller tail; dequeue drops front if it leaves', 3),
