  ('prep-stacks-queues-implement-stack-with-min::pattern', 'prep-stacks-queues-implement-stack-with-min', 'Which approach fits "Implement stack with min"?', 'Each node carries the running min beside its value', 0),
  ('prep-stacks-queues-implement-stack-with-min::key-step', 'prep-stacks-queues-implement-stack-with-min', 'On the "POP" step (popped ), what happens?', 'Returned . The stack is back to  cell(s); the running-min of the new top is already correct, no recomputation needed.', 1),
