  ('prep-stacks-queues-trapping-rain-water::pattern', 'prep-stacks-queues-trapping-rain-water', 'Which approach fits "Trapping Rain Water"?', 'Two pointers `l=0, r=n-1`, track `maxL` and `maxR`', 0),
  ('prep-stacks-queues-trapping-rain-water::init', 'prep-stacks-queues-trapping-rain-water', 'At the start of a run (Trapping Rain Water), what strategy is established?', 'Trapping Rain Water: each bar is a wall of the given height; water pools in the dips between taller walls. Two pointers l=0 and r= close inward, tracking maxL and maxR — the tallest wall seen from each side.', 1),
