  ('prep-strings-count-words-obtained-after-adding-a-letter::init', 'prep-strings-count-words-obtained-after-adding-a-letter', 'At the start of a run (Count Words Obtained After Adding a Letter), what strategy is established?', 'Each word is reduced to a 26-bit mask (bit k set if letter ''a''+k appears). A target is obtainable when removing exactly one of its letters yields a mask that exists in the start-word set. Build that set first.', 1),
