  ('prep-trees-print-side-view::init', 'prep-trees-print-side-view', 'At the start of a run (Print side view), what strategy is established?', 'Right-side view: standing to the RIGHT of the tree, we see only the last node on each level. We BFS level by level; on every level the final node dequeued (i === sz − 1) is the one we can see.', 1),
