  ('prep-trees-recover-binary-search-tree::pattern', 'prep-trees-recover-binary-search-tree', 'Which approach fits "Recover Binary Search Tree"?', 'In-order traversal of a valid BST is sorted. Two swapped nodes create inversions.', 0),
